        <rdfs:comment xml:lang="en">Population of a place. Uses these properties: populationTotal, year (when measured, populationYear), rank (sortOrder of this place amongst its siblings at the same level), name (areal measured by the population, eg: &quot;locality&quot;, &quot;municipality&quot; or &quot;comitat&quot;)</rdfs:comment>
